(2, 'About Electronic Payment Systems', 'About Electronic Payment Systems', 'Headquartered in Denver, Colorado, Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is one of the nation''s oldest and largest merchant service providers.', '<p>Headquartered in Denver, Colorado, Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is one of the nation&#39;s oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers of electronic payment products to businesses and ISO&rsquo;s. Uniquely positioned in the payments industry, EPS provides a comprehensive suite of merchant processing solutions, the highest level of data security, and expertise to drive revenue and profitability for all business types including retailers, restaurants, hotels, automotive, healthcare, service businesses, e-Commerce and non-profit organizations.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>EPS Electronic Payment Processing Advantages:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Security and Peace of Mind:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS continues to be on the forefront of adopting new data security measures including the implementation of Payment Card Industry Data Security Standards (PCI DSS) before it was a requirement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cash flow:</strong>-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide access to funds within 48 hours at rates which are among the best in the industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Service:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talk to a real person! In-house customer service and technical support is available 24/7/365 - meaning your business never has to experience a down time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company&#39;s turnkey and integrated electronic payment solutions include&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing" target="_blank">credit card processing</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing" target="_blank">check verification</a>, <a href="/check-processing" target="_blank">check conversion and check guaranty services</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways" target="_blank">online transactions</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/gift-card-program" target="_blank">gift and loyalty cards</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/cash-advance" target="_blank">cash advances</a>&nbsp;and the revolutionary&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan" target="_blank">No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a>, our patented in-house payment plan of up to $5000 over 90-days with no credit check required enabling merchants to increase their customer base and revenues.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>EPS Fast Facts:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Over 25 years&rsquo; experience in the payments processing industry</li>\r\n	<li>Processes payments for more than 150,000 businesses</li>\r\n	<li>$5 million in processing volume per day</li>\r\n	<li>More than 400 affiliate partners nationwide</li>\r\n	<li>Privately-held corporation headquartered in Englewood, Colorado</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>EPS Awards &amp; Accolades:-</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&lsquo;A+&rsquo; rated with&nbsp;<a href="http://www.bbb.org/denver/business-reviews/credit-card-a-merchant-services/electronic-payment-systems-in-englewood-co-23001241" target="_blank">Better Business Bureau</a></li>\r\n	<li>2011 Best Electronic Check Processing Company from Top Credit Card Processors</li>\r\n	<li>2012&nbsp;<a href="http://www.prweb.com/releases/2012/3/prweb9254725.htm" target="_blank">Best Electronic Check Processing&nbsp;</a>Company from Top Credit Card Processors</li>\r\n	<li>2011 Best Online Credit Card Processing Companies from Top Credit Card Processors</li>\r\n	<li>2012 Best Online Credit Card Processing Companies from Top Credit Card Processors</li>\r\n	<li>2012&nbsp;<a href="http://www.stevieawards.com/pubs/sales/awards/426_2281_21508.cfm?" target="_blank">GOLD STEVIE WINNER:</a>&nbsp;Customer Service Team of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>2012&nbsp;<a href="http://www.stevieawards.com/pubs/sales/awards/426_2281_21508.cfm" target="_blank">BRONZE STEVIE WINNER:&nbsp;</a>Technical Support Team of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>2014 BRONZE STEVIE WINNER: Customer Service Team of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>2014 SILVER STEVIE WINNER: Sales Team of the Year</li>\r\n	<li>2015 <a href="http://www.marketwatch.com/story/fifty-best-credit-card-processing-services-revealed-in-april-2015-by-topcreditcardprocessorscom-2015-04-12" target="_blank"> Best Online Credit Card Processing</a>&nbsp; From Top Credit Card Processors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way! Ready to learn more about which electronic payment solution is best for your business? Call&nbsp;1-800-863-5995&nbsp;for a no obligation&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis.</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 2, 'Headquartered in Denver, Colorado, Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is one of the nation''s oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers of electronic payment products to businesses and ISO’s. Uniquely positioned in the payments industry, EPS provides a comprehensive suite of merchan', 'About Electronic Payment Systems', 'About Electronic Payment Systems', 'Located in Denver, Co. Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is one of the nation''s oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers of electronic payment products to businesses and ISO’s.', 1, '', '', 'pasture', 'jpg', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'The #1 Credit Card Processor for over 20 Years.', '#eeeeee', 'center', 1, '2015-07-31 18:00:41', '2015-09-14 13:16:04'),
(3, 'Services We Provide', 'Services We Provide', '', '<p>Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is a leading, privately held merchant service provider delivering the most cost-effective, innovative and technologically advanced electronic payment processing in the industry. We create customized solutions with our unique products to drive revenue and increase profitability for all business types including retailers, restaurants, hospitality, service professionals, healthcare services, e-commerce, utility companies, MOTO and non-profit organizations.</p>\r\n', 11, 'Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is a leading, privately held merchant service provider delivering the most cost-effective, innovative and technologically advanced electronic payment processing in the industry. We create customized solutions with our unique products to drive revenue and increase pro', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'As a leading privately held merchant credit card processing company, we deliver the most cost-effective, innovative and technologically advanced electronic payment processing in the industry.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-01 06:14:59', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(4, 'Industries We Serve ', 'Industries We Serve ', '', '<p><strong>Electronic Payment Systems (EPS)</strong>&nbsp;delivers the most innovative, technologically advanced payment processing solutions with the highest level of data security. Our comprehensive suite of merchant services include&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">credit card processing</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing">check verification, conversion &amp; guaranty services</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/wireless-solutions">online transactions</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/gift-card-program">gift and loyalty cards</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/cash-advance">cash advances</a>&nbsp;and the most revolutionary alternative payment product in the industry, our patented&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a>, an in-house payment plan of up to $5000 over 90-days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every industry has its own challenges and requirements for accepting electronic payments; there is no one solution fits all. EPS provides customized payment processing solutions that are cost-effective, safe and secure to meet the specific needs of each business. We specialize in helping small and medium sized merchants gain a competitive advantage in the marketplace by not only offering low cost credit card processing but also unique programs which increase customers, stimulate growth and boost profitability for businesses just like yours.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="/small-businesses">Small Business</a>&nbsp;&ndash; increase overall sales by offering multiple payment options such as debit and credit card processing in addition to increasing customers and growing business with&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="/retail-stores">Retail</a>&nbsp;&ndash; provide customers with more flexibility by offering multiple payment options and increase up-selling potential</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/restaurants">Restaurants</a>&nbsp;&ndash; deliver customer convenience while better managing cash flow; process tip included transactions, no signature (or receipt) required for QSR&rsquo;s and&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">pay at the table&nbsp;</a>solutions.</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/hospitality">Hospitality</a>&nbsp;&ndash; simplify guest reservations and check-in by accepting payments face-to-face, over the telephone or online.</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/service-professionals">Service Professionals</a>&nbsp;&ndash; offer convenient payment options, increase customer service, decrease risks and reduce overhead costs associated with paper checks</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/healthcare-services">Healthcare Services</a>&nbsp;&ndash; increase collections, reduce loss, and reduce billing related expenses by accepting electronic payments at time of appointment, schedule recurring payments, and offering&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="/utility-companies">Utility Companies</a>&nbsp;&ndash; expand payment options, increase customer service and decrease operational costs</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/e-commerce">Internet/e-Commerce</a>&nbsp;&ndash; real-time processing of electronic payments via your website with data secure solutions that integrate with all major shopping carts</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/moto-solutions">MOTO</a>&nbsp;&ndash; accept electronic payments via mail order or telephone for product and service deliveries without investing in POS hardware</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/non-profit-&amp;-charitable">Non-Profit / Charitable Organizations</a>&nbsp;&ndash; accept electronic payments for event registration, initiate supporter donations via your website, offer recurring payment options and increase donation amounts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS makes accepting electronic payments fast, easy, secure and affordable. We take pride in exceeding our merchants&rsquo; expectations in delivering unsurpassed service and living up to our philosophy of&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;The Customer Comes First&rdquo;</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn which credit card processing solution is best for your business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis.</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 24, 'Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) delivers the most innovative, technologically advanced payment processing solutions with the highest level of data security. Our comprehensive suite of merchant services include...', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'We deliver the most innovative, and technologically advanced payment processing solutions with the highest level of data security, confidently providing services to a range of industries.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-11 14:15:43', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
