itcardprocessorscom-2015-04-12" target="_blank"> Best Online Credit Card Processing</a>&nbsp; From Top Credit Card Processors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way! Ready to learn more about which electronic payment solution is best for your business? Call&nbsp;1-800-863-5995&nbsp;for a no obligation&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis.</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 3, 'Headquartered in Denver, Colorado, Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is one of the nation''s oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers of electronic payment products to businesses and ISO’s. Uniquely positioned in the payments industry, EPS provides a comprehensive suite of merchan', 'About Electronic Payment Systems', 'About Electronic Payment Systems', 'Located in Denver, Co. Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) is one of the nation''s oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers of electronic payment products to businesses and ISO’s.', 1, '', '', 'homepage_hi_0', 'jpg', '', '', '#605d5d', 'center', 1, '2015-08-11 14:40:04', '2015-09-08 13:30:56'),
