sa Travelers Checks</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="/pdfs/dataAuditing.pdf" target="_blank">Data Auditing Notice</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Video Tutorials:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="/videos" target="_blank">Benefits of EPS 90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="/videos" target="_blank">EPS Testimonial</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="/videos" target="_blank">How To Run a EPS 90 and Single Check Transaction</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="/videos" target="_blank">How To Setup The Elite II and RDM 6014</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><big>For List of Certified Security Assessment Companies:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.visa.com/cisp" target="_blank">www.visa.com/cisp</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.mastercard.com/sdp" target="_blank">www.mastercard.com/sdp</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 35, 'Merchant Resources', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Merchant Resources: EPS Merchant Application EPS Processing Agreement Articles EPS Lease Agreement General Information Articles:', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-11 14:49:34', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(7, 'Executive Summary', 'Executive Summary', '', '<p><strong>Electronic Payment Systems </strong>is the quintessential American success story. What began as an idea to improve credit card processing blossomed into a growing business, one that continues to grow and evolve. We operate our business today with the same philosophies under which we created the company back in 1994: The customer comes first! We live and breathe this by bringing you the latest and most secure technologies, from our mobile processing solutions to the most innovative alternative payment product in the industry, our patented&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>John Dorsey &ndash; Founder / CEO</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>John Dorsey is an accomplished CEO with years of success in growing businesses from the ground up, beginning his career in the payments industry in the mid 80&rsquo;s as a sales agent offering credit card processing services to businesses. At that time, only Credit Card Acquiring traditional banks offered this service and getting merchants approved was extremely difficult as most banks did not want to take the risk. John&rsquo;s strong entrepreneurial spirit, combined with strategic insight and foresight, led him to the challenge of overcoming bank obstacles, enabling &ldquo;Merchant Services&rdquo; to be marketed and sold on a much broader basis. He was instrumental in the rapid development of the Merchant Service Provider /Independent Sales Organization (ISO) industry that exists today. To this day, he remains active in the businesses he creates, living and breathing the philosophy which all of his businesses were built on: The customer comes first!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Tom McCann &ndash; Founder / Managing Partner</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Tom McCann is a serial entrepreneur with extensive corporate management experience who has taken numerous small businesses and turned them into large, profitable companies. His specialties include operations management, transaction processing solutions, mergers and acquisitions and contract negotiations. Tom has served in executive capacities for over a dozen companies, becoming involved in the payments industry while he was principal of a lease funding company in the late 80&rsquo;s. Tom is engaged in the high level strategic planning and execution of EPS contract negotiations, developing strategic alliances with leading banks, processors, ISO&rsquo;s and vendors in the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The combination of Tom&rsquo;s financial management background and John&rsquo;s credit card processing sales expertise created the perfect alliance. In 1994, they co-founded ElectCheck guaranty which turned into EPS today, one of the oldest and largest privately held Merchant Service Providers in the industry. ElectCheck opened the door to the creation of our patented&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan </a>program which allows merchants to offer their customers a payment plan for up to $5000 over a 90 day period with no credit check required. EPS has since become one of the most profitable Merchant Service Providers in the nation in an extremely competitive industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Anthony Maley &ndash; Chief Operating Officer</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Anthony S. &ldquo;Tony&rdquo; Maley is our Chief Operating Officer and has been in the merchant services industry and EPS for fifteen-(15) years. Tony started as a MLS for a company in Cleveland, Ohio, which is where he met John Dorsey, Tony quickly determined that he could do much more than just outside sales, and as fortune has it John felt the same way. A friendship was formed that lives on today. Tony by nature is analytical and practical at the same time. He has a unique talent for gleaning reality from data, and works well with the banks and processors he is required to deal with on a regular basis. His responsibilities include general oversight of all EPS operations and specific project management of others. He maintains the accounts for EPS and reconciles settlement data with the bank. Mr. Maley is a member of the ETA and NACHA and has served on several committees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We at EPS never forget our roots. We started as a small business and like you we had BIG dreams. We know first-hand what challenges you face and are going to be with you every step of the way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn more about which electronic payment solution is best for your business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 4, 'Electronic Payment Systems is the quintessential American success story. What began as an idea to improve credit card processing blossomed into a growing business, one that continues to grow and evolve. We operate our business today with the same philosophies under which we created the company back ', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Executive Summary', 'Electronic Payment Systems is the quintessential American success story. What began as an idea to improve credit card processing blossomed into a growing business, one that continues to grow and evolve. We operate our business today with the same philosophies under which we created the company back in 1994: The customer comes first!', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-12 15:01:35', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(8, 'ISO Program', 'Partners: Independent Sales Organization (ISO) Program', '', '<p>As one of the oldest and largest privately-owned merchant service providers in the nation, we are able to offer the most flexible and personalized ISO program in the industry.&nbsp;<a href="/about-eps">EPS</a>&nbsp;provides our ISO and Agent Partners an infrastructure with many advantages:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Revenue Share:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>EPS offers the most competitive cost structure in the industry</li>\r\n	<li>Residuals paid on ALL revenue streams</li>\r\n	<li>Extremely low merchant attrition rate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Support &amp; Service:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>EPS puts your needs first to create win-win situations that are both profitable now and durable into the future stimulating on-going growth of your business</li>\r\n	<li>All-inclusive ISO training session on how to open and run a successful office</li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive monthly sales training and daily webinar trainings for your sales representatives</li>\r\n	<li>Dedicated Agent Relations, Sales Support, Underwriting, Risk Management, Retention, Customer Service &amp; Technical Support departments all handled by experienced in-house by employees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Peace of Mind:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>EPS&nbsp;<a href="/executive_summary">Executive Team</a>&nbsp;has been in the merchant service industry for over 25 years, our experience and comprehensive knowledge simply can&rsquo;t be matched, &ldquo;We&rsquo;ll Show You The Way!&rdquo;</li>\r\n	<li>Highest level of data security with&nbsp;<a href="/pci-compliance">PCI Compliant&nbsp;</a>solutions</li>\r\n	<li>24/7 Award-winning customer service and technical support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Tools &amp; Technology:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Quick and easy electronic applications</li>\r\n	<li>Convenient online residual reporting</li>\r\n	<li>Innovative&nbsp;<a href="/mobile-payments">Mobile Processing solution</a></li>\r\n	<li>Personalized website and emails</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/auth/login">Agent Portal</a>&nbsp;to track &lsquo;real time&rsquo; application status</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Competitive Advantage:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Full range of&nbsp;<a href="/industries">electronic payment processing solutions for all industries</a></li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive suite of&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">credit card processing products</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing">check conversion services</a>&nbsp;specifically designed to give you a competitive advantage</li>\r\n	<li>Price Match Guarantee and&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">Free Statement Analysis&nbsp;</a>offered</li>\r\n	<li>98% approval rate of new merchant accounts within 48 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are dedicated to providing our ISO&rsquo;s and Agents with the personalized attention your growing business needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Want to learn more? Call 1-800-863-5995 today.</p>\r\n', 5, 'As one of the oldest and largest privately-owned merchant service providers in the nation, we are able to offer the most flexible and personalized ISO program in the industry. EPS provides our ISO and Agent Partners an infrastructure with many advantages:\r\nRevenue Share\r\nSupport & Service\r\nPeace of ', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Partners: Independent Sales Organization (ISO) Program   As one of the oldest and largest privately-owned merchant service providers in the nation, we are able to offer the most flexible and personalized ISO program in the industry. EPS provides our ISO and Agent Partners an infrastructure with many advantages:', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-12 15:05:57', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(9, 'Merchant Referral', 'Merchant Referral', '', '<p><strong>EPS&#39;</strong>&nbsp;philosophy &ldquo;The customer comes first&rdquo; has led us to becoming one of the largest merchant service providers across the country so we designed the Referral Program as a way to say &ldquo;Thank You&rdquo; to all our merchants who have made this possible. You don&rsquo;t have to be a merchant to join though, everyone is eligible and there are no limits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Making extra money with our Referral Program is as easy as 1-2-3:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1. Tell your friends, family and business associates about us by mentioning our&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">Low Price Guarantee with Free Statement Analysis</a></li>\r\n	<li>2. Fill out a&nbsp;<a href="/pdfs/referralCoupon.pdf">Referral Program</a>&nbsp;coupon</li>\r\n	<li>3. Receive $50 for each referral that signs up with us</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We know you&rsquo;ll always want to tell your friends, family and business associates about getting low credit card processing rates and best customer service in the industry for many years to come and we want to continue to thank you so there is no limit to the amount of referral bucks you can earn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On top of you earning a referral fee, your friends and family now have the opportunity to save money on their credit card processing too, so it&rsquo;s a win-win! Your referrals also gain the following benefits when switching to EPS:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Partner with a single source provider for all merchant service needs with&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">credit card processing</a>,<a href="/check-processing">check verification, conversion &amp; guaranty services</a>,&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a></li>\r\n	<li>In-house, award winning customer service and technical support 24/7/365 ensuring sales are never lost from downtime</li>\r\n	<li>Customized solutions creating the most effective and efficient solutions for each specific businesses needs</li>\r\n	<li>Enjoy peace of mind with the highest level of data security&nbsp;<a href="/pci-compliance">PCI Compliant</a>&nbsp;solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Latest, most technologically advanced electronic payment processing equipment from&nbsp;<a href="/counter-top-terminals">POS</a>&nbsp;and<a href="/wireless-solutions">wireless terminals</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">online processing</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="/mobile-payments">mobile solutions</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking for lower credit card processing rates for your business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 6, 'Making extra money with our Referral Program is as easy as 1-2-3:\r\n\r\n1. Tell your friends, family and business associates about us by mentioning our Low Price Guarantee with Free Statement Analysis\r\n2. Fill out a Referral Program coupon\r\n3. Receive $50 for each referral that signs up with us\r\n', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'EPS'' philosophy “The customer comes first” has led us to becoming one of the largest merchant service providers across the country so we designed the Referral Program as a way to say “Thank You” to all our merchants who have made this possible. You don’t have to be a merchant to join though, everyone is eligible and there are no limits.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-12 19:27:29', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(10, 'Give Back Program ', 'Give Back Program ', '', '<p>Our focus at&nbsp;<strong>Electronic Payment Systems (EPS)</strong>&nbsp;has always been to deliver the best credit card processing solutions for all types of businesses while also providing unique solutions to increase sales and help growth. Throughout the years, we&rsquo;ve also been committed to supporting charitable organizations and have thus created a special Give Back Program to increase contributions to the non-profit sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The EPS Give Back Program is a free fundraiser for non-profit organizations. It&rsquo;s a unique way for non-profits to effortlessly raise significant funds towards their charity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&quot; We are proud to team with EPS for this new and exciting program that will give back to our organization&quot; said Jody McKay, Co-Founder and Director of Pink Ribbon Riders. &quot;We are also on track to save 20% for the year! That&rsquo;s more money our organization can focus to patients in need. &quot;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Joining the Give Back Program is as easy as 1-2-3:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1. Quick &amp; easy sign-up &ndash; just give us a call &amp; we&rsquo;ll have your non-profit set-up within 72 hours or less</li>\r\n	<li>2. Invite friends, family &amp; supporters to join</li>\r\n	<li>3. Earn 10% of processing profits every month from every business that joins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s that simple! Once a business signs-up under your organization, you receive 10% of their processing profits every month for the life of their account. Your charitable organization will earn substantial additional funds for your group effortlessly each and every month.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Benefits for businesses joining the Give Back Program:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Totally free &ndash; donation amount comes from EPS&rsquo; profit so it doesn&rsquo;t cost the business anything</li>\r\n	<li>Increase contributions &ndash; supporters are now able to contribute additional financial aid to your organization</li>\r\n	<li>Convenient &ndash; donation is automatically sent to non-profit organization every month so it&rsquo;s never late or forgotten</li>\r\n	<li>Decreased costs - low credit card processing rates backed by our&nbsp;<a href="http://www.eps-na.com/free_statement_analysis">Price Match Guarantee</a>&nbsp;enables business to save money</li>\r\n	<li>Contributions are tax deductible for business</li>\r\n	<li>Credibility &ndash;&nbsp;<a href="/about-eps">EPS&nbsp;</a>is one of the nations&rsquo; oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers in the industry providing customized, secure and low cost payment processing for over 20 years</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity &ndash; merchants can increase customers &amp; grow business with our patented&nbsp;<a href="/give-back">EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a>, in-house payment plan allowing your customers to get up to $5000 of the products and services they need today while paying for it over a 90 day period</li>\r\n	<li>Technologically advanced - comprehensive suite of products including&nbsp;<a href="/counter-top-terminals" target="_blank">POS terminals</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/wireless-solutions">Wireless Solutions,</a>&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">Virtual Terminals,</a>&nbsp;<a href="/check-readers">Check Acceptance Readers,</a>&nbsp;<a href="/gift-card-program">Gift Cards</a>, and our newest mobile processing solution&nbsp;<a href="/mobile-payments">EZ Pay Mobile</a></li>\r\n	<li>Peace of mind &ndash; the highest level of data security backed by PCI compliant solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Exceptional service &ndash; in-house, award-winning Customer Service and Technical Support departments available 24/7/365</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&quot; This program enables businesses to provide additional financial assistance to a charitable organization on a regular basis without costing them anything. In fact, they will actually save money when we beat their current processing rates&quot; said John Dorsey, CEO of EPS &quot;It&rsquo;s a way for us to help non-profit organizations earn significant funds for their charities. &quot;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to start earning additional funds for your non-profit organization? Call 1-800-863-5995 to join EPS Give Back Program today!</p>\r\n', 8, 'Our focus at Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) has always been to deliver the best credit card processing solutions for all types of businesses while also providing unique solutions to increase sales and help growth. Throughout the years, we’ve also been committed to supporting charitable organizatio', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'We&#039;ve been committed to support charitable organizations and as a part of that, we have created a special Give Back Program to increase contributions to the non-profit community.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-12 19:28:22', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(11, 'Testimonials', 'Testimonials', '', '<p>As one of the oldest &amp; largest merchant service providers in the nation, EPS equips &amp; processes electronic payment transactions for thousands of merchants each year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="/videos">Click Here</a>&nbsp;to view actual unsolicited video testimonial from our clients &ndash;they speak for themselves! Then submit your information for a Free Statement Analysis to see what EPS can do for your business!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Thank You Letters From Our Merchants:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Dentist - Raleigh, NC</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being a dentist I have always used Care Credit, and I have been turning away 3 or more patients almost every week. Now I can actually do business with everyone who comes into my clinic no matter how much credit they have or don&#39;t have. I&rsquo;m glad to have found a payment plan to offer our patients so we can give them the dental care they need without having to worry about whether or not we will be getting paid.&nbsp;<strong>We love the program.</strong><br />\r\n<strong><em>&ndash; Jessica S., Accounts Receivable</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Tire &amp; Rim Shop - Baltimore, MD</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We installed the EPS90 system 1 year ago and it has more than exceeded our expectations. We have a new motto now: &quot;Everyone gets tires!&quot; Not only have the overall sales of our tires have gone up, but our up-sells of rims has&nbsp;<strong>increased almost 30% in the past year.</strong><br />\r\n<strong><em>- Don D.</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Remodeler - Boston, MA</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>My company has been with Electronic Payment Systems for about 5 years. We have utilized MC/VS quite effectively in our business. About a year ago, our sales agent stopped by and introduced us to the EPS90 payment plan with no credit check needed. This has been a godsend. We sold over $100,000.00 in new jobs using the EPS90, our salespeople use a portable system for laptops while they are on location which makes our bidding &amp; sales process extremely convenient. We are doing about 4 to 5 jobs a month where offering the EPS90 no credit check payment plan has been the deciding factor.&nbsp;<strong>We love you guys, Thank You!</strong><br />\r\n<strong><em>- Frank D, Owner</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Agent and ISO Thoughts About EPS:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><big>EPS Agent - Pawtucket, RI</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am an independent agent with EPS and have been working with the company for almost 7 years now. I&rsquo;ve been in sales all my life but have never found a company that cared so much about the success of its agents. From the beginning, the product &amp; industry training was superb, and the one on one attention they provided really helped me to start selling quickly. Everyone at the company from the sales dept. to agent relations to customer service to tech, everyone has been very helpful and a pleasure to work with. They also really care about their merchants &amp; go above &amp; beyond to keep them happy with award-winning customer service and tech support. I feel confident knowing that when I sign up a new merchant they are going be taken care of for years to come. And offering the patented EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan gives me a competitive advantage as it allows me to provide a real solution for business owners. The fact that not only does EPS always save merchants money on their processing but also provide something that no one else in the industry does, a way to actually boost their business, is awesome. It&rsquo;s a win-win for every business I talk to which makes my job one that I love to do. I now make a steady 6 figure income &amp; am no longer worried about my finances.<strong>Thanks for everything EPS!</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>- Jack M., Regional Sales Manager, NE Region</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>EPS of Washington &ndash; Agent Office</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;ve been a part of the EPS family for over 15 years as one the first sales agents with John Dorsey. Having mastered all of the EPS corporate trainings and gaining an in-depth knowledge of the merchant service industry, I became fully vested in under 3 years &amp; opened my own Independent Sales Office. EPS gave me more than a job, they truly delivered the opportunity of a lifetime. Today I provide thousands of small to larger businesses all of their merchant service processing needs. Being with EPS allows me to really help my clients by offering them the best customer service, the lowest rates, and the most innovative solutions in the industry.<br />\r\n<strong><em>&ndash; Kim B., EPS of Washington Agency Office Owner</em></strong></p>\r\n', 9, 'As one of the oldest & largest merchant service providers in the nation, EPS equips & processes electronic payment transactions for thousands of merchants each year.\r\n\r\nClick Here to view actual unsolicited video testimonial from our clients –they speak for themselves! Then submit your information f', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'As one of the oldest and largest merchant service providers in the nation EPS equips and processes electronic payment transactions for merchants each year.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-12 19:29:30', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(12, 'Merchant Credit Card Processing Solutions', 'Processing Solutions for Merchants', '', '<p>Providing the latest, most technologically advanced credit card processing solutions and equipment with the highest level of data security to our merchants. We know the importance of efficiency when running a business, especially small businesses starting out. Our goal is to make it quick and easy for you to establish a&nbsp;merchant service account&nbsp;and get your business prepared with the right equipment. With EPS, your business can be ready to accept electronic payments in 2 hours or less.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Electronic Payment Systems takes care of all your merchant solution needs, customizing the best rate structure and processing solution to fit your specific business requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="/mobile-payments">Mobile credit card processing</a>&nbsp;for businesses on the go</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/counter-top-terminals">POS terminals</a>&nbsp;for retail, restaurants and service businesses</li>\r\n	<li>Over 2 decades of experience in helping <a href="/small-businesses">small businesses</a>.</li>\r\n	<li><a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">Virtual terminals</a>&nbsp;for online processing</li>\r\n	<li>Support for numerous payment gateways that connect with your shopping cart</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless solutions for&nbsp;<a href="/moto-solutions">MOTO credit card transactions</a></li>\r\n	<li>Plus, our patented&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why EPS?</h2>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>FEATURES</td>\r\n			<td>EPS</td>\r\n			<td>COMPETITORS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Deposit Funding</strong></td>\r\n			<td>1-2 business days</td>\r\n			<td>3-4 business days</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Rate Structure</strong></td>\r\n			<td>*Interchange Plus &amp; Tiered Pricing*</td>\r\n			<td>Tiered Pricing</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Set-Up Fee</strong></td>\r\n			<td>None</td>\r\n			<td>$195 &amp; up</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Approval Rate</strong></td>\r\n			<td>98% Approval Rate</td>\r\n			<td>60% Approval Rate</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Approval Time</strong></td>\r\n			<td>4-24 Hours</td>\r\n			<td>1-3 weeks</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Service &amp; Support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>24/7/365 Live, US Based Service (In-house)</td>\r\n			<td>Automated Outsourced to third party</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>*</strong>EPS uses whichever rate structure is best for your business type; we provide each merchant with a customized payment processing solution<strong>*</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Learn which credit card processing solution is best for your business. <strong><a href="/contact_eps">Contact us online</a></strong>&nbsp;or call 1-800-863-5995 to speak to an EPS Representative today!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 12, 'Providing the latest, most technologically advanced credit card processing solutions and equipment with the highest level of data security to our merchants. We know the importance of efficiency when running a business, especially small businesses starting out. Our goal is to make it quick and easy f', 'Electronic Payment Systems', '', 'Grow your business with confidence. We provide merchants with credit card processing solutions that make it easy to obtain payments from your customers.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'center', 1, '2015-08-13 16:52:55', '2015-09-08 14:44:53');
