(13, 'Mobile Payment Solutions: Simple Credit Card Processing On The Go', 'Accept Credit Card Payments Through Mobile Processing', '', '<p>Electronic Payment Systems gives you&nbsp;the ability to accept payments through your mobile phone fast and easy while having the peace of mind with&nbsp;<a href="/pci-compliance">data security</a>. With mobile processing being more quickly and securely, our new&nbsp;<strong>EZ Pay Mobile</strong>&nbsp;payment solution is a step above the rest and receive a FREE merchant credit card reader when you sign up. There are many benefits involved that will help your business; being large or small, with our mobile payment technology. Check out the following features that are available:</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>FEATURES</td>\r\n			<td>EPS EZ PAY</td>\r\n			<td>SQUARE</td>\r\n			<td>INTUIT GO!</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Use as POS system</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Signature capture</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Purchase, tax, tips, custom receipts</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Void transaction</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Refund/credit to customer</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Inventory tracking</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Manage cash transactions</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Quick deposits $1000 and up</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Voice Recognition System (Vlingo)</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Real time management system</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Store and forward (when cellular service not available)</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Downloadable format for easy bookkeeping</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Check verification &amp; conversion</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan program</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Free Mobile Device</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>24/7/365 Live Person Customer Support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>X</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our <strong>mobile processing payment technology</strong> not only far out-weighs the competition&#39;s capabilities, it is also more cost-effective, making it one of the best portable credit card reader to choose from. Get started activating your mobile payment reader from any iPhone, Android smartphone device or tablet instantly. Simply complete the&nbsp;<a href="/pdfs/EPS Merchant Application Cash.pdf">merchant application</a>&nbsp;to obtain a mobile merchant account with EPS; providing us with your account information for deposits, the type of cell phone device you will be using and the phone number to be associated with EZ Pay Mobile reader. Once approved, EPS will overnight ship the EZ Pay credit card reader device with easy instructions and you&#39;ll be ready to accept mobile payments on your smartphone in no time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As with all our products and services, if you need assistance installing the mobile account application, completing the activation or need training on proper usage, a highly trained representative of our technical support department is available 24/7 to provide further assistance. We are committed to staying true to the EPS philosophy&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;The customer comes first!&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn more about which mobile merchant account service offers the best gateway for your business or need additional information on mobile payments and how to get started accepting credit cards through your phone? Fill out the simple information below or call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation <em>FREE Statement Analysis</em> and quickly see how much we can help you save.</p>\r\n', 13, 'Electronic Payment Systems gives you the ability to accept payments through your mobile phone fast and easy while having the peace of mind with data security. With mobile processing being more quickly and securely, our new EZ Pay Mobile payment solution is a step above the rest and receive a FREE me', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'mobile payments, accept credit cards by phone, payments on smartphone', 'Accept mobile credit card processing with Electronic Payment Systems. Take payments quick and easy through your mobile iPhone and Android devices safely and securely. Learn how, sign up today with our mobile merchant account', 1, '', '', 'sliding-credit-card-on-ipad-device', 'jpg', '', '', '#fffdfd', 'center', 1, '2015-08-13 17:13:20', '2015-09-08 15:59:45'),
(14, 'Wireless Payment Solutions ', 'Wireless Payment Solutions ', '', '<p><strong>Electronic Payment Systems (EPS)</strong>&nbsp;understands that many businesses need the ability to accept payment transactions while on the go or in the field. Our wireless credit card processing machines provide flexible, reliable, and secure portable electronic payment processing when traditional connections aren&rsquo;t available. It&rsquo;s the perfect solution for:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Service professionals such as plumbers, landscapers, HVAC specialist &amp; home repair companies</li>\r\n	<li>Businesses that attend tradeshows</li>\r\n	<li>Non-profit organizations who organize charitable events</li>\r\n	<li>Mail order/ telephone order (MOTO) businesses</li>\r\n	<li>Consultants who conduct business out of others&rsquo; homes such as <strong>Mary Kay&trade;, Avon&trade;, Pampered Chef&trade;, Scentsy&trade; and PartyLite&trade;&nbsp;</strong>representatives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS offers the most technologically advanced wireless credit card processing solutions enabling you to maintain a competitive edge in today&rsquo;s evolving market:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability to accept electronic payment transactions anytime, from any location</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid equipment costs by using your existing PC, Web browser and wireless or Internet connection as a&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">payment gateway</a></li>\r\n	<li>Sales never lost due to internet connectivity issues</li>\r\n	<li>Increases cash flow and decreases administrative overhead costs</li>\r\n	<li>Flexibility to send transactions individually or on a daily batch basis</li>\r\n	<li>Convenient online reporting available making it easy to reconcile payments</li>\r\n	<li>Highest level of data security with PCI compliant solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Low processing rates backed by our&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">Price Match Guarantee</a></li>\r\n	<li>In-house, award-winning Customer Service and Technical Support departments with calls answered by a live person 24/7/365</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to offering a variety of wireless credit card terminals and payment solutions to choose from, EPS has several other processing methods available to mobile businesses including virtual terminals, phone based software applications for your iPhone or Blackberry and our newest&nbsp;<a href="/mobile-payments">mobile processing solution</a>&nbsp;EZ Pay Mobile. EPS specializes in providing customized solutions to best fit your business; enjoy a single source merchant service provider for all your payment processing needs with&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">credit card processing</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing">check conversion services</a>, and our patented&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way to Hassle Free Wireless Credit Card Processing!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn which Wireless Solution is best for your business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>.</p>\r\n', 14, 'Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) understands that many businesses need the ability to accept payment transactions while on the go or in the field. Our wireless credit card processing machines provide flexible, reliable, and secure portable electronic payment processing when traditional connections a', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'wireless payment solutions, payment processing, wireless credit card processing, process electronic payments', 'Our wireless credit card payment solutions provides flexible, reliable and secure point of sale payment system from traditional readers that aren&#039;t available.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-13 17:32:40', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(15, 'Virtual Terminals and Gateways', 'Virtual Terminals and Gateways', '', '<p><strong>EPS</strong>&nbsp;assists thousands of online businesses everyday with their e-commerce payment transactions by offering the most technologically advanced virtual terminal solutions in the industry. EPS utilizes Authorize.net, eProcessingNetwork and UsaEPay Payment Gateways to provide the complex infrastructure and security necessary to ensure fast, reliable and secure transmission of transaction data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many of our customers combine our Technology Partners&#39; Payment Gateways with Internet-enabled point-of-sale systems to gain an end-to-end solution that far surpasses dialup systems in efficiency and reliability. IP-based Point of Sale (POS) systems offer several advantages:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Increase customer satisfaction by speeding up lines at the register &amp; making checkout faster</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce costs by consolidating broadband service costs &amp; eliminating multiple telephone lines</li>\r\n	<li>Boost reliability as payment gateway performance is continuously monitored</li>\r\n	<li>Enjoy quick &amp; easy real-time online reporting by simply logging onto a secure website portal &amp; entering your password</li>\r\n	<li>Immediately access transaction status as it becomes available - anytime, anywhere</li>\r\n	<li>Peace of mind with redundant systems across all geographic regions backing up the processing environment</li>\r\n	<li>Increase stability, ensuring processing at all times, even if you are experiencing a temporary Internet outage</li>\r\n	<li>Has all the characteristics of a Desktop and POS terminal</li>\r\n	<li>Highest level of data security with <a href="/pci-compliance">PCI compliant</a> solutions</li>\r\n	<li>In-house, award-winning customer service and technical support available 24/7/365</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS offers customized payment processing solutions for all types of businesses, whether you are a retail storefront, restaurant, hotel/motel, service professional, medical office, utility company, e-Commerce store, MOTO business, or non-profit organization we are dedicated to providing the best solution for your specific credit card processing needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn which electronic payment solution will best support your business model? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>.</p>\r\n', 15, 'EPS assists thousands of online businesses everyday with their e-commerce payment transactions by offering the most technologically advanced virtual terminal solutions in the industry. EPS utilizes Authorize.net, eProcessingNetwork and UsaEPay Payment Gateways to provide the complex infrastructure a', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'virtual terminals, gateway payments', 'EPS assists thousands of online businesses everyday with their e-commerce payment transactions by offering the most technologically advanced virtual terminal solutions in the industry.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-13 17:55:22', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
