(18, 'Merchant Cash Advance Programs ', 'Merchant Cash Advance Programs ', '', '<p><strong>EPS</strong>&nbsp;understands how businesses operate and know that there are many times when procuring additional cash is crucial. Whether for new equipment, advertising, remodeling or expansion, inventory re-stock, or to pay off debts, we make it easy for you to attain the essential funds you need with merchant cash advances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Realizing the difficulty and frustrations of trying to qualify for a small business loan, we&rsquo;ve partnered with Rapid Advance to offer our merchants a quick, easy and cost-effective funding solution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Befefits of the EPS Merchant Cash Advance Programs</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Higher approval rates than bank loans and&nbsp;<strong>more money</strong>&nbsp;than competitors</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Lower cost</strong>, no points or up-front fees and minimal credit requirements</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Flexible repayment</strong>&nbsp;process depending on your sales volume rather than being tied to fixed monthly payments</li>\r\n	<li>Simple application and&nbsp;<strong>quick approval process</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; pre-approval within 24 hours</li>\r\n	<li><strong>No interest, security or collateral taken</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>no collateral liens</strong>&nbsp;(UCC-1) filed so there are no restrictions placed on your ability to access additional financing</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Faster funding</strong>&nbsp;gives you the money you need in as little as 10 days</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Advantages of Becoming an EPS Merchant</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Credibility</strong>&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;<a href="/about-eps">EPS</a>&nbsp;is one of the nations&rsquo; oldest and largest, privately held merchant service providers in the industry providing customized, secure and low cost electronic payment processing solutions for over 20 years</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Security</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Enjoy peace of mind with the highest level of data security backed by&nbsp;<a href="/pci-compliance">PCI compliant solutions</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Affordability</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Save money with low processing rates backed by our&nbsp;<a data-target="#myModal" data-toggle="modal" href="#myModal">Price Match Guarantee</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Payment Solutions</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Enjoy a single source merchant service provider for all your payment processing needs with&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">credit card processing</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing">check conversion services</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/gift-card-program">gift cards</a>, and more!</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Comprehensive Products</strong>&nbsp;&ndash;<a href="/counter-top-terminals">&nbsp;POS terminals </a>,<a href="/wireless-solutions">Wireless Solutions</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">Virtual Terminals</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/check-readers">Check Acceptance Readers</a>, and our newest&nbsp;<a href="/mobile-payments">mobile processing</a>&nbsp;solution EZ Pay Mobile</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Support</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; In-house, award-winning Customer Service and Technical Support departments with calls answered by a live person 24/7/365</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter how old your business is, unexpected expenses and hard times can leave you in need of immediate working capital. Being able to secure a merchant cash advance may mean the difference between surviving the hard times or closing your doors for good. Merchant cash advance can also give your small business the edge it needs to succeed in a highly competitive market. Whatever situation your business is experiencing, a merchant cash advance from EPS can be just the push your business needs to strengthen and gain momentum.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Looking for a business loan and need cash fast? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a Merchant Cash Advance today!</p>\r\n', 18, 'EPS understands how businesses operate and know that there are many times when procuring additional cash is crucial. Whether for new equipment, advertising, remodeling or expansion, inventory re-stock, or to pay off debts, we make it easy for you to attain the essential funds you need with merchant ', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'merchant cash advance programs, cash advance, ez pay, merchant programs, cash advance', 'Making it easy for you to attain the essential funds you need with our merchant cash advance programs offering benefits such as lower costs and flexible payments.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-13 18:33:37', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(19, 'Merchant Gift Card Program', 'Merchant Gift Card Program', '', '<p>A crucial aspect of every business is keeping its current customers happy while continually gaining new customers and increasing sales. We understand the unique challenges of competing with larger retailers and specialize in providing customized payment solutions designed to increase customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gift card programs for small business help to boost sales by not only bringing in new customers but also by increasing each sale&#39;s total and encouraging repeat visits. They are also a cost-effective and affordable marketing medium for building brand loyalty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Benefits of Merchant Gift Card Programs:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>1. Expand customer base</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; almost 50 million adults purchased gift cards for their friends/ family in the last year</li>\r\n	<li><strong>2. Increase sales</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; 61% of consumers often spend more money than the gift card&#39;s original face value amount</li>\r\n	<li><strong>3. Build brand loyalty</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; both existing and new customers become more connected to your business</li>\r\n	<li><strong>4. Boost up-selling</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; adding gift cards at your check-out counter inspires customers to purchase for their friends/ family</li>\r\n	<li><strong>5. Decrease cost</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; it&#39;s more efficient to issue gift cards electronically compared to manually creating gift certificates</li>\r\n	<li><strong>6. Increase efficiency</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; gift cards are electronically charged and funded through your&nbsp;<a href="/counter-top-terminals">credit card processing terminal</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>7. Timesaving</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; electronic &ldquo;stored value&rdquo; function automatically updates unused balance eliminating the need to reissue</li>\r\n	<li><strong>8. Convenient</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; ability to reissue a lost gift card if consumer has kept the original purchase receipt</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We&rsquo;ve partnered with Tender Card, a pioneer of gift card processing and loyalty programs, to offer the most cost-effective gift cards available, with quantities as low as 100 cards for smaller merchants who don&#39;t require as many cards as national chains.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Gift Card Facts &amp; Trends:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As gift cards become increasingly more convenient, personalized and sought after, retailers can expect to see a significant increase in gift card sales this year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>According to the National Retail Federation:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gift card sales are forecasted to increase 5.7% to $217.4 billion, representing the largest increase since 1999</li>\r\n	<li>48% of consumers are planning to purchase at least one pre-paid card or gift certificate this year and 29% of consumers will buy three or more</li>\r\n	<li>Of those planned purchases, 35% will spend $25-$30 on each card while 25% will spend $50 or more</li>\r\n	<li>48% of consumers said they would like to receive gift cards this year, up from 41% the previous year</li>\r\n	<li>Gift card sales this holiday season are forecasted to total $26.3 billion, compared to $24.8 billion in 2006</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn how Merchant Gift Card Programs can help your small business grow? Call 1-800-863-5995 today!</p>\r\n', 19, 'A crucial aspect of every business is keeping its current customers happy while continually gaining new customers and increasing sales. We understand the unique challenges of competing with larger retailers and specialize in providing customized payment solutions designed to increase customers....', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'merchant gift card program', 'A crucial aspect of business is keeping its current customers happy while continually gaining new customers and increasing sales. We understand the unique challenges of competing with larger retailers and specialize in providing customized payment solutions designed to increase customers. Merchant gift card programs for small business help to boost sales by not only bringing in new customers but also by increasing each sales total and encouraging repeat visits. They are also a cost-effective and', 1, '', '', 'cardSwipe-_lo', 'jpg', '', '', '', 'center', 1, '2015-08-13 18:39:07', '2015-09-08 16:05:55'),
(20, 'High Risk Merchant Credit Card Services and Merchant Accounts', 'High Risk Merchant Credit Card Services and Merchant Accounts', '', '<p>Is your business having trouble getting approved for traditional merchant service accounts? Do you need a High Risk Merchant Account? EPS offers a full suite of electronic payment solutions for all business types, including high risk merchant service needs. We have high risk merchant account offices across the US to help you with your needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>High risk merchants are those businesses which fall outside conventional categories, have an increased risk of fraud, a high turnover rate, or a high credit rate. They typically have a hard time being approved for credit card processing and are often declined when applying for merchant credit card service accounts. The &ldquo;High Risk Merchant&rdquo; label makes it a real challenge for many honest and hardworking merchants to process credit card transactions resulting in reduced popularity, decreased customers, plummeting sales, and ultimately lost revenue. EPS understands that accepting electronic payments is as vital for survival to high risk merchants as it is for every other business, and with our philosophy of &ldquo;The customer comes first&rdquo;, we have a solution that is right for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just because your industry may be unconventional, doesn&#39;t mean you should have to continually deal with the hassle of finding a credit card processor to work with. We offer merchant credit card services that specialize in High Risk Merchant Accounts for the following industries:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>E-Commerce</li>\r\n	<li>Online Dating</li>\r\n	<li>Health and Beauty</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-level Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Adult Entertainment</li>\r\n	<li>Nutraceuticals</li>\r\n	<li>Traveling</li>\r\n	<li>Business Opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>Tobacco/ Cigarette Products</li>\r\n	<li>And many more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS can get your High Risk merchant account approved 