(23, 'Check Acceptance Readers', 'Check Acceptance Readers ', '', '<p><strong>EPS&nbsp;</strong>has been providing merchants with the tools needed to protect against fraud, NSF check acceptance and the high fees associated with accepting paper checks for payment. All provided while increasing the businesses profitability and reducing cost rates, living up to our philosophy of&nbsp;<em>&ldquo;The Customer Comes First!&rdquo;</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Partnering with EPS for your businesses&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">check conversion services&nbsp;</a>has many unique advantages over competitors including:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Faster cash turn-around</li>\r\n	<li>Improved cash flow with funds deposited directly into your bank account</li>\r\n	<li>Protection against bad check acceptance</li>\r\n	<li>Guarantee option assures face value payments once check is approved</li>\r\n	<li>Reduced overhead cost associated with chasing bad check writers</li>\r\n	<li>Eliminates risk &amp; costly fees of NSF checks</li>\r\n	<li>Simplified POS accounting</li>\r\n	<li>Opportunity to increase sales &amp; grow your business by adding our patented alternative payment option EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan (link to EPS90 page), in-house payment plan allowing your customers to get up to $5000 of the products and services they need today while paying for it over a 90 day period</li>\r\n	<li>Enjoy a single source merchant service provider for all your payment processing needs with credit card processing, check conversion services, our patented EPS90 No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan and our newest mobile processing solution EZ Pay Mobile</li>\r\n	<li>Highest level of data security with PCI compliant solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Low processing rates backed by our Price Match Guarantee</li>\r\n	<li>In-house, award-winning Customer Service and Technical Support departments with calls answered by a live person 24/7/365</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Our preferred check reader machine for converting paper checks at the point of sale is RDM&rsquo;s Digital Imaging Solution (link to RDM&rsquo;s product brochure) compatible with all major terminals (link to terminal list).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS specializes in providing customized solutions to best fit your business needs and makes it easy for you to establish a merchant service account (link to Merchant Services). Gain a competitive advantage by offering your customers the most payment options available in the marketplace while decreasing your cost of processing with EPS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn which equipment is best for your business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>.</p>\r\n', 23, 'EPS has been providing merchants with the tools needed to protect against fraud, NSF check acceptance and the high fees associated with accepting paper checks for payment. All provided while increasing the businesses profitability and reducing cost rates, living up to our philosophy of “The Customer', 'Electronic Payment Systems', 'check readers, check verification services, acceptance readers, check verification systems, check acceptance readers, nsf checks', 'Providing merchants with tools in protecting against fraud with our check acceptance readers allowing businesses to eliminate the risk and costly fees of NSF checks.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-14 06:38:55', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(24, 'Small Businesses Credit Card Processing', ' Merchant Accounts for Small Business', '', '<p>Congratulations! You&#39;ve successfully entered into the world of business ownership. You are ready to start accept payments from your customers. The challenge is you need to find a reliable and secure&nbsp;<a href="/services">small business merchant service provider</a>&nbsp;to offer your customers with as many payment options as possible. So where do you start when you want to accept payments? It may seem a daunting task with so many different processing companies pushing small businesses with processing services, but don&#39;t get discouraged. We realize that you are an expert in your trade field; however, the world of how small business credit card processing works is probably not an area of interest so we&#39;re here to help.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>What To Look For In A Credit Card Processing Company?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Although establishing a merchant account is a fairly quick and easy process, avoid making a careless decision when choosing a payment processor. Do not base your decision solely on the current marketing incentives of free equipment or advertised low rates as the overall costs, and customer service provided are much more important in the long run. Choose a company with these following questions:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Will they be around for the long-term?</strong><br />\r\n	Choose an actual Merchant Service Provider (MSP) with credibility and longevity in the industry. MSP&rsquo;s also typically provide lower rates and better service as well since there are no middleman.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Do they have a full suite of services?</strong><br />\r\n	EPS offers a full suite of electronic payment processing solutions to meet all of your business needs. We will even customize a solution to best fit your business needs.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Do they have the latest security protocols?</strong><br />\r\n	We continue to be a leader by incorporating the highest level of data security and adhering to all PCI Compliance standards.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Do they have around the clock customer service?</strong><br />\r\n	Problems never arise when its &ldquo;convenient&rdquo;, you never know when a technical issue may arise and you don&rsquo;t want to lose sales over it. EPS provides in-house customer service and technical support departments 24/7/365 to ensure your business never has a down moment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We make it easy for small businesses to establish a&nbsp;<a href="/high-risk">merchant service account</a>&nbsp;and accept all forms of electronic payment transactions including&nbsp;<a href="/credit-card-processing">debit and credit card processing</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing">checks</a>, and&nbsp;<a href="/gift-card-program">gift cards</a>. We even go a step further in helping your business grow with our patented&nbsp;<a href="/ez-payment-plan">No Credit Check EZ Payment Plan.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS is a full service merchant service company that has been an integral part of the electronic payment industry since the very beginning. We&#39;ve earned an A rating from the Better Business Bureau (BBB), have won multiple awards for our Customer Service and Technical Support departments and have been providing the highest level of data security meeting PCI standards before it was even a requirement. Electronic Payment Systems processes payments for over 150,000 businesses, from large to small.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>Let EPS Show You The Way!</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ready to learn more about which small business credit card processing solution is best for your business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 25, 'Congratulations! You''ve successfully entered into the world of business ownership. You are ready to start accept payments from your customers. The challenge is you need to find a reliable and secure small business merchant service provider to offer your customers with as many payment options as poss', 'Electronic Payment Systems', '', 'Preparing your small business to secure credit card transactions easier. Start accepting payments quicker and let your business succeed. Contact us today to get started.', 1, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '2015-08-14 06:56:43', '2015-09-08 15:06:46'),
(25, 'Retail Payment Solutions', 'Payment Solutions for Retail', '', '<p><strong>Electronic Payment Systems (EPS)</strong>&nbsp;assist thousands of businesses everyday with their point of sale systems (POS), merchant services and helps process payments for purchases in a retail environment. Whether you are a clothing store, furniture store, automotive shop, salon, or mall kiosk, EPS can customize your retail payment solution for your specific business needs. There are many reasons a retail business should offer merchant service options in today&rsquo;s technological environment:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Customers not only enjoy the flexibility but actually expect the accessibility of various payment options</li>\r\n	<li>Removes limitations of making a sale with customers who may not have enough cash on hand</li>\r\n	<li>Entices customers to increase their total purchase when given the option of paying with their debit or credit card</li>\r\n	<li>Provides opportunity to up-sell every customer at point-of-sale</li>\r\n	<li>Streamlines your businesses cash flow</li>\r\n	<li>Reduces the handling of cash</li>\r\n	<li>Reduces the risk associated with accepting paper checks</li>\r\n	<li>Creates additional marketing opportunities with&nbsp;<a href="/gift-card-program">gift cards and loyalty program</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For traditional point of sale retail credit card processing needs, a&nbsp;retail merchant account&nbsp;enables you to authorize, settle and manage electronic transactions from your retail store using a variety of connectivity methods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let EPS Show You The Way!<br />\r\nReady to learn more about which electronic payment solution is best for your retail business? Call 1-800-863-5995 for a no obligation&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">FREE Statement Analysis</a>&nbsp;and see how much you can save.</p>\r\n', 26, 'Electronic Payment Systems (EPS) assist thousands of businesses everyday with their point of sale systems (POS), merchant services and helps