(26, 'Restaurant Payment Processing', 'Restaurant Payment Processing', '', '<p><strong>EPS&nbsp;</strong>serves a full menu of electronic payment solutions for all types of restaurants, from casual and fine dining establishments to fast food and quick service restaurants (QSR). We realize that every second counts when serving your customers and know the importance of providing quick and efficient service so we work with you to find the best restaurant payment processing solution. Accepting debit and credit card payments in your restaurant has several benefits:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Reduces the amount of cash employees need to handle</li>\r\n	<li>Offers convenience to your customers</li>\r\n	<li>Manages your cash flow through automatic bank deposits</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>EPS understands the importance of managing your cash flow and your business, providing speedy deposits to your bank account while being compatible with the majority of hospitality management systems. Regardless of the system you are currently using, EPS can simply connect to it as your electronic payment provider.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><big>Processing Tip-Included Transactions</big></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Most customers prefer leaving a tip in the same tender they used to pay for their bill. There are many details to know on processing a transaction with a tip, including how to enter in the tip amount after running the transaction before batching out at the end of day. Talk with your EPS representative regarding how to properly, effectively and efficiently process tips. You can rest assured when partnering with EPS for all your&nbsp;Merchant Payment Processing&nbsp;needs as our in-house customer service and technical service departments are available 24/7/365.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><big>No Signature Required</big></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>QSR&rsquo;s can qualify to process transactions under $25.00 without requiring a customer signature. The No Signature restaurant credit car