(32, 'Payment Processing for Non-Profit / Charitable Organizations', 'Payment Processing for Non-Profit / Charitable Organizations ', '', '<p>The ability for non-profit organizations to accept electronic payment transactions is proven to dramatically increase overall donations according to a recent survey published in Payments Market (June 2012). The study showed a 239% increase in charitable donations at fundraisers that accepted debit and credit cards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Partnering with EPS for non-profit credit card processing allows you to:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><big>1. Increase donations/revenues:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Encourages automatic and reoccurring contributions via automated credits</li>\r\n	<li>Customizable&nbsp;<a href="/give-back">Give Back Programs</a></li>\r\n	<li>Increases donation amounts as people tend to donate more when their charity accepts credit cards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><big>2. Decrease operating costs:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Reduced overhead costs and risk associated with accepting paper checks</li>\r\n	<li>Low non-profit payment processing rates backed by our&nbsp;<a href="http://www.eps-na.com/free_statement_analysis">Price Match Guarantee</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><big>3. Peace of mind:</big></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Partner with EPS, a single source provider for all your electronic payment transactions with&nbsp;<a href="#myModal">credit card processing</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="/check-processing">check verification&nbsp;</a>services</li>\r\n	<li>Customized non-profit merchant services and solutions with convenient and flexible options available including&nbsp;<a href="/wireless-solutions">wireless terminals</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/virtual-terminals-and-gateways">online processing</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="/mobile-payments">mobile solutions</a></li>\r\n	<li>Protect your donor data with PCI compliant non-profit payment processing solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Experience award-winning customer service and technical support available 24/7/